Package org.ceu.alf.ecollections

org.ceu.alf.ecollections is a package that contains all the stuff required to manage ontologies that use the E-Collection ontology.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ElementOfWrongTypeException
    Exception thrown when trying to add an element to an homogeneous collection and the element not belongs to the ontology class of the elements of the collection.
    ExistingUriException
    Exception thrown when trying to create a new entity with an URI already used in the ontology.

Package org.ceu.alf.ecollections Description

org.ceu.alf.ecollections is a package that contains all the stuff required to manage ontologies that use the E-Collection ontology.
